One-Room Shelter Analysis

An analysis of damage to One Room Shelters, post 2022 floods in Pakistan

Author

IOM

Published

23 October 2022 17:20

Introduction

This analysis is based on assessments of a sample of 350 villages in Sindh in which One Room Shelters were built in 2012 and 2013.

The interactive map below shows the survey locations approximated within an 36km2 area to preserve privacy.
